111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c3002%2c20221013%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,3002,20221013,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"3002","JDATE":"20221013","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}